### ALS subtype expansion (v2 land 2026-05-10 — `.roadmap.disease_als_specific` v2) — 3 DESIGN candidates

axonal common pathway sync — CMT2 axonal + ALS motor neuron axon paradigm 공유. HDAC6 chemotype = CMT(말초 한정 P-gp 회피) ↔ ALS(CNS 침투 필수) 정반대 → 별도 ID 분기. SARM1 chemotype = CMT 와 동일 (TIR/ARM domain 보존), separate ID 는 BBB audit tracking 용. C9orf72 = ALS-specific (CMT 무관).

