| `hxq-als-sar1-001`    | als     | SARM1 TIR NAD+ pocket reversible inhibitor (Wallerian-like 축삭변성) | 경구 소분자 (BBB audit Phase β)       | Q    | 17    | `Nc1nc2cc(F)c(F)cc2c(=O)n1Cc1ccncc1` (CMT chemotype 동일, BBB 침투 audit 별도) | DESIGN |
| `hxq-als-nano-001`    | als     | Motor neuron-targeting nanocarrier (IT, modular cargo: SOD1 ASO / hxq-als-{hd6,sar1,c9orf72}-001 / SMN2 splice mod) | PLGA-PEG hybrid 50-80nm + ChAT/SMI-32 ligand | NB | n/a | PLGA-PEG + ChAT/SMI-32 motor neuron 선택 ligand + IT delivery + pH-responsive PEG-shedding + retrograde axonal transport assist (kinesin-1) — Phase β specify | DESIGN |
