## 5. Phase plan

### Phase A — Initial design land (cycle 108) ✓ COMPLETE
- 5 entry skeleton + naming convention
- SMILES specified (derivation 명시)

### Phase B — Build + VQE (cycle 111) ✓ COMPLETE ⭐⭐⭐
- 5/5 novel drugs all sub-µHa
- hxq-gen-001 0.026 µHa = NEW LIBRARY BEST (paper-rounding limit territory)
- F-Q-6-B-real path universality 검증 (FDA + de novo 모두 동일 path)

### Phase C — Pocket supersystem (Tier 1 ramp F-Q-6-D) — IN-PROGRESS

#### Attempt 1: 자동 frontier-orbital ActiveSpaceTransformer (cycle 113) — honest-fail
- methyl_acrylate (Michael acceptor) + methyl_thiol (Cys mimic) supersystem
- 자동 2e/2o ActiveSpaceTransformer 가 fragment HOMO+LUMO 와 supersystem HOMO+LUMO 에 다른 orbital mapping
- E_int = E(super) − E(acrylate) − E(thiol) = +5308 kcal/mol (physically nonsensical, wrong sign + magnitude)
- 진단: apples-to-oranges 2e/2o 비교 — interaction energy 계산 invalid

#### Attempt 2: 4e/4o UCCSD on supersystem (cycle 113-114) — IN-PROGRESS
- cycle 85 H2O 4e/4o UCCSD chem-acc 0.6338 mHa PASS 의 자연 진화
- 4e/4o = 4 frontier orbitals → 두 fragment 의 HOMO+LUMO 모두 cover 가능
- UCCSD ansatz (chemistry-aware Trotter cluster operator)
- 결과 도착 시 land

#### Attempt 3+ (TBD): 추가 candidates
- explicit orbital indices selection (chemistry judgment)
- full FCI without active-space reduction (very small system 만)
- 8e/8o + UCCSD (larger active-space)
- explicit pocket residue active-space (Cys145 + His41 + ligand reactive 부분 — F-Q-6-D-1 nirmatrelvir target)

### Phase D — Library ranking (Tier 1 ramp F-Q-6-F)
- 각 target 마다 5-10 candidate library
- Spearman vs known FDA inhibitor

### Phase E — VQE-guided generative refinement
- low-binding candidates 에 대한 atom modification
- iterative chem-space exploration

### Phase F — disease-specific subtype expansion (cycle TBD — ongoing)
- CMT 10-candidate land 2026-05-10 (`.roadmap.disease_cmt_specific` v2)
- ALS 3-candidate land 2026-05-10 (`.roadmap.disease_als_specific` v2 — axonal common pathway sync, hd6/sar1 CMT chemotype divergence audit + c9orf72 ALS-specific)
- 향후 disease entry 의 신약-우선 rebuild 시 본 file 에 row 추가

---

## 6. raw#10 honest C3

1. **SMILES "derivation" 은 existing scaffold 의 simplification/modification** — 진정한 de novo (scaffold-free) 가 아님. 첫 cycle 의 scope 한정. 진정한 de novo = generative model (chemical-language-model 또는 RL) + VQE binding score reward; 본 roadmap 의 Phase E 가 그 scope.
2. **isolated molecule VQE = infrastructure 검증** — Phase B 만 으로는 wet-lab 의미 없음. Phase C (pocket supersystem) 가 진정한 binding affinity entry.
3. ~~**Lipinski rule-of-5 검증 없음 (cycle 108 entry)**~~ → **§8 Lipinski Ro5 audit (v6 land 2026-05-10)** — CMT/ALS placeholder SMILES 5종 hand-heuristic Ro5 audit PASS. rdkit 정밀 audit (TPSA / RotB / formal charge) 는 추후 ramp.
4. **target-tag 의 chemistry judgment 한정** — 본 cycle 의 target-tag 는 known FDA-target 와 동일; 새 target discovery 는 별도 scope.
5. **wet-lab validation 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, 임상 의미 없음.
6. **CMT 10-candidate (v2 2026-05-10)** — 부작용 회피 7-axis design constraint 위에서 land. SMILES 4 종 (hd6/clc1/sar1/mfn2) = scaffold simplification placeholder, 6 종 (pmp22-001/002, gjb1-001, nrg1-001, fig4-001, nano-001) = schematic only. "부작용 없는" 절대 보장 불가 — known liability avoidance 까지가 honest scope (`.roadmap.disease_cmt_specific` v2 §9-1 참조).
7. **ALS 3-candidate (v2 2026-05-10)** — axonal common pathway sync. `hxq-als-hd6-001` = CMT 후보의 polar acid → methyl 치환 → CNS-penetrant variant (CMT 말초 한정 paradigm 정반대). `hxq-als-sar1-001` = CMT chemotype 동일, BBB audit 별도 ID 분기. `hxq-als-c9orf72-001` = ALS-specific (BIIB078 ASO fail 후 small-mol paradigm shift). 모두 wet-lab 0건 + Lilly/Disarm SARM1 chemotype IP-회피 의무.
8. **ALS goal-saturation v4 (2026-05-10)** — 4 subagent 병렬 audit 후 NANOBOT axis 강화: `hxq-als-nano-001` (PLGA-PEG hybrid 50-80nm + ChAT/SMI-32 motor neuron ligand + IT + pH-shed + modular cargo) land. CMT nano-001 (Schwann perineurium ligand) 와 분기 — same modality class (PLGA-PEG), different ligand + delivery (peripheral injection vs intrathecal). RIBOZYME 다양화 비목록(STMN2 ASO QurAlis QRL-101 + ATXN2 ASO Stanford-Lilly + ADAR RNA-editing) = 후속 design 권장.
9. **ALS goal-saturation v5 (2026-05-10)** — RB+Q axis 후보 직접 land: `hxq-als-kif5a-001` (motor protein stabilizer, axonal 3-way rescue cluster HDAC6+SARM1+KIF5A 완성) + `hxq-als-stmn2-001` (TDP-43 cryptic exon ASO, QurAlis QRL-101 comparator) + `hxq-als-atxn2-001` (polyQ ataxin-2 ASO, Stanford-Lilly comparator) + `hxq-als-tbk1-001` (LoF rescue chaperone, discovery-stage). KIF5A scaffold class novel (kinesin chemistry) + TBK1 LoF rescue chemistry novel — 둘 다 honest disclaimer "discovery-stage chemistry novel" 추가. STMN2/ATXN2 ASO = 표준 gapmer paradigm (DTx/Ionis 선례).

---

## 7. Cumulative cycles

6 cycles. Initial 5 entry skeleton land 2026-05-07 (cycle 108). CMT 10-candidate batch land 2026-05-10 (v2). ALS 3-candidate batch land 2026-05-10 (v2 axonal sync). ALS goal-saturation v4 land 2026-05-10 (nano-001). ALS goal-saturation v5 land 2026-05-10 (kif5a/stmn2/atxn2/tbk1). **v6 Lipinski Ro5 audit land 2026-05-10** (§8 — 5 placeholder SMILES hand-heuristic audit PASS, rdkit 정밀 audit ramp 대기). Library 34 drugs total.

